          "insert": "#D9D9D9",
          "attributes": {
            "code": true
          }
        },
        {
          "insert": " border, 30px height, 12px horizontal padding, 16px text, and font weight 700. In document order the hit path paints first, then the visible path, then the label chip, then selected bend pills/endpoints, so bend chrome is layered above labels when they compete."
        }
      ],
      "children": []
